HEADWORD: Techy
<hw>Tech"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From OE.
<ets>tecche</ets>, <ets>tache</ets>, a habit, bad habit, vice, OF.
<ets>tache</ets>, <ets>teche</ets>, a spot, stain, blemish, habit, vice,
F. <ets>tache</ets> a spot, blemish; probably akin to E. <ets>tack</ets>
a small nail. See <er>Tack</er> a small nail, and cf.
<er>Touchy</er>.]</ety> <def>Peevish; fretful; irritable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

